+def greet(name: str) -> str:
     print("Hello, " + name)

Apply changes? [y/N]: y
‚úì Applied changes

File 2/5: src/api.py
--- original
+++ modified
-def fetch_data(url):
+def fetch_data(url: str) -> dict:

Apply changes? [y/N]: y
‚úì Applied changes

‚úì Completed: 5 files modified

lite-code > !
